NAME
  windows::pause - Waits for a specified duration

SYNOPSIS
  windows::pause( duration )

PARAMETERS
  duration  - specified in milli seconds

DESCRIPTION
  The function waits for the specified number of milli seconds.

EXAMPLES
  >>(windows::beep(500+k*100,100),windows::pause(100)) $ k=1..10
  ...

